{"tid":2420982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【新時代文字獄】革除陋习 復興中華！","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T17:12:16.000Z","uid":293677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd654fc5e9232a9712f4c5d7a09745fffee64d4","tid":2420982,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>避諱習近平？網瘋傳中國標語「陋習」被改成「陋刃」</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/22/phpNBw6HF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F22%2FphpNBw6HF.jpg&h=348a0e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國標語在網路瘋傳，，只見簡體字的<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「陋习」被改成「陋刃」</span></span>，讓不少網友認為這是在避諱習近平的「习」。（圖擷自@GFWfrog推特）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/22 11:31<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕太誇張！推特上近來瘋傳一張照片，只見在中國某處的標語寫著「提高文明衛生水平 革除陋習」，其中陋習的簡體字「陋习」被改成「陋刃」，讓不少網友認為這是在避諱習近平的「习」。<br />\n<br />\n從推特照片可以看到，這則標語就在修車廠前面的路燈柱上，簡體字全文為<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">「提高文明卫生水平 革除陋刃」</span></span>，但最後這個「革除陋刃」讓人看得滿頭問號，直到思考一番才驚覺原來是替換掉簡體的「陋习」。<br />\n<br />\n目前不清楚標語的實際地點，但從修車廠招牌都是簡體字看來，應該是在中國境內無誤。另外，若實際上到微博搜索，無論是繁體的「陋習」或簡體的「陋习」都查不出任何結果，不過在一些中國入口網站如新浪等等，用「陋習」或「陋习」都能查到使用這兩字的新聞，因此尚無法確定將「陋习」改成「陋刃」的背後原因。<br />\n<br />\n推特上許多網友則猜測這應該就是避諱了，笑稱「陋習避慶豐帝諱（習近平過去前往北京慶豐包子鋪營造親民形象，但也成為習包子一詞的起源），改為陋刃」，不少人也認真地指出，避諱通常是少寫一筆，所以「陋刁」才是對的，還有網友不禁感嘆，這樣一來《論語》恐怕要改成「學而時刃之，不亦說乎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3445530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3445530&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmwwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=251364b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3445530&h=75acc580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3445530</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">革除陋<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">习</span></span> 復興中華！</span></span>"},{"pid":"159050dcf8f3d6b8723dcb2d66aaa14af0463927","tid":2420982,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"中國式新語"},{"pid":"c177b41b217e1f2056b8e6c7c5a85726410359f7","tid":2420982,"uid":112551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"變革香港 革除陋习 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0a96893461376b6aaa14f8618af68bc523ce30","tid":2420982,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"革除陋习 變革香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c6fd588ce2cbd2c04c8a5f0587ca980759ac82","tid":2420982,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c177b41b217e1f2056b8e6c7c5a85726410359f7","tid":2420982,"uid":112551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"變革香港 革除陋习 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05be507882bdf8a58e57118f29fe6df9c238854a","tid":2420982,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c177b41b217e1f2056b8e6c7c5a85726410359f7","tid":2420982,"uid":112551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"變革香港 革除陋习 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />革除陋习 復興香港！<br />\n<br />\n實現香港偉大復興！"},{"pid":"bfd01ef4999675b48740f449e8df8c7f6fd341c8","tid":2420982,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c177b41b217e1f2056b8e6c7c5a857